                            <para>ZTSE2780</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <graphic id="g05002b4" filename="../figg05/G05002B4.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1"
                                     scalefitwidth="192px" scalefitheight="192px"/>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Power Steering Analyzer - Comes complete with flared tube connectors and female swivel
                                fitting hoses. The analyzer is designed for measuring power steering pump flow rate and
                                pump pressure. The analyzer includes a one to ten gallon-per-minute flow rate and 0 to
                                3,000 pound range pressure gauge. It is supplied with two quick couplings on the
                                analyzer's hoses for connecting to the hydraulic system. To install, disconnect high
                                pressure line at either the power steering pump or steering gear and connect analyzer
                                into the high pressure line. Includes storage case and instruction on how to use.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>ZTSE4230</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
