                                     scalefitwidth="192px" scalefitheight="192px"/>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Spring Tension Scale (0-25 lbs.) - Used to measure pitman arm backlash, as well as
                                pinion bearing preload.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
